      "citation_id": "[CITATION_6]",
      "span_text": "The non-denatured deglycosylated JRFL gp140 Env bound well to mAb 2G12 and also bound to DC-SIGN. In this regard, the gp120 high mannose residues involved in 2G12-gp120 binding have been reported to be involved in gp120-DC-SIGN binding [CITATION_6] .",
